  "subject": "Add snapshot deploy to pom.xml",
  "commit_message": "Add snapshot deploy to pom.xml\n\nCurrent so/libs release\nartifact is depending on\nmissing version of oparent 1.1.0-SNAPSHOT.\n\nThis change attempts to enable snapshot\nbuilds so that SO builds can be based on\nworking snapshots rather than non working\nrelease builds.\n\nIssue-ID: SO-533\nChange-Id: I3a78a0f7fc0a25753c23a265cd4b4e05ec0a0e14\nSigned-off-by: Marcus G K Williams <marcus.williams@intel.com>\n",
